---

## Summary Table

| Use Case | Route | Description |
|----------|-------|-------------|
| 📋 Lister hobbies | `GET /hobbies` | Display all hobbies with status & progress |
| ➕ Ajouter hobby | `POST /hobbies` | Create new hobby (name required) |
| 🔄 Toggle status | `PATCH /hobbies/{id}/toggle` | Switch active ↔ paused |
| 🗑️ Supprimer hobby | `DELETE /hobbies/{id}` | Delete a hobby |
| 📈 Modifier niveau | - | Update skill level |
| ⏱️ Modifier fréquence | - | Set daily/weekly/monthly |
| 😀 Ajouter emoji | - | Custom emoji icon |
| 📝 Description | - | Detailed hobby description |
| 📊 Progression | - | Track 0-100% progress |
| 📈 Statistiques | - | View hobby stats |

---

## Model Fields

| Field | Type | Default | Description |
|-------|------|---------|-------------|
| name | string | required | Hobby name |
| level | string | 🎯 Débutant | Skill level |
| frequency | string | 📅 Quotidien | Practice frequency |
| status | string | active | active or paused |
| emoji | string | - | Custom emoji |
| progress | integer | 0 | 0-100% |
| description | text | - | Details |

---

## Routes

```
GET     /hobbies              → index()
POST    /hobbies              → store()
PATCH   /hobbies/{id}/toggle  → toggle()
DELETE  /hobbies/{id}         → destroy()
```

---

